  "FriendlyName": "Beam Platform Notifications",
  "Description": "Cross-engine notifications SDK: local + remote push, deep links, templates, action buttons, rich media, and Beamable funnel analytics (configureAuth + native funnel POSTs for offer Clicked/Converted tracking). iOS (Swift core via C ABI) + Android (Kotlin core via JNI).",
